name: Preset File
summary: Learn about .PJUNOXL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: The PJUNOXL file will be located in the "Presets" folder in the application directory.

description: Preset file used by TAL-U-NO-LX, a synthesizer instrument emulator; contains pre-made or customized audio settings for an instrument sample such as "Disco Bass," "DRM Kick Drum 1 FMR," and "WND Clarinet FMR;" includes settings for volume, midi clock sync, voice hold, octave transpose, velocity volume, and more.
